data.title: I Ought To Be in Pictures Study Guide
data.meta_description: I Ought to Be in Pictures Study Guide - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Libby Tucker, a 19-year-old from Brooklyn, arrives unannounced in Los Angeles to visit her brother Herb, a struggling screenwriter. She meets Steffy Blondell, Herb's girlfriend, and hopes to break into acting. Libby attends auditions but struggles in the cutthroat world of 1970s Hollywood. Her optimistic attitude clashes with Herb's cynical view of the industry.
